Comment:
 This project originated as a fork of
 https://github.com/hifiberry/snapcastmpris (MIT licence, declared via
 the upstream setup.py classifier; no LICENSE file shipped at upstream).
 The shipped source files are a complete rewrite around asyncio,
 python-snapcast and dbus-fast and contain no code from the upstream
 repository. HiFiBerry is acknowledged in the README as the origin of
 the design.

